  "notes": [
    "This study used an in vitro triple-culture model with Caco-2, HT29-MTX-E12, and THP-1 cells to investigate ST3Gal1's role in intestinal barrier function",
    "ST3Gal1 appears to negatively regulate intestinal barrier function through modulation of barrier-protective proteins and inflammatory mediators",
    "The study provides evidence for ST3Gal1 as a potential therapeutic target in ulcerative colitis"
  ]
